{"tid":1379200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前 線 戰 術 必 須 改 變","createTime":"2019-07-28T18:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:45:23.000Z","uid":2140,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"afe29e2b435d519476721b6a129fb9b5768ada35","tid":1379200,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"前線失策既地方有兩個：<br />\n1. 停留 2. 死守<br />\n完全放棄左示威者流動既優勢。<br />\n正面同班狗抗衡，除非我地有molotov，否則死硬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，班狗係郁得好撚慢的。<br />\n中上西環大量內街，<br />\n如果前線既大家都叫齊身邊既手足去繞後﹑包抄﹑轉位<br />\n班狗係唔會夠人，亦唔會夠快去驅散到我地<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要保持流動，拒絕留守<br />\n要打就打游擊戰同巷戰，唔好有同full gear 既狗正面砌。"},{"pid":"7453b6535cc21ee0f090aec6e38a6d91efc8b51f","tid":1379200,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7148f8ce2fbba1dcf0abf1aa5c6384d6eb664b18","tid":1379200,"uid":13638,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:01:48.000Z","msg":"前線唔係驚狗 唔係冇裝 係驚法律責任"},{"pid":"bdd63b626f75c863e3ffad7522d5f4e11bc65eeb","tid":1379200,"uid":187387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好火遮眼, 見到有人放策略就盲目正評<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一個叫人入青衣油庫既送頭post竟然過5000 like</span></span><br />\n請大家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好入</span></span></strong>青衣!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">[撥亂反正] 反對入青衣</span></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/drQRzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/drQRzS</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">搞青衣比搞香港任何地方都更加危險, 千其唔好中伏</span></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378493</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">[香港地理] 入青衣比狗圍死 搞機場皆大歡喜</span></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378405</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style